cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "melis x402 Tools (@melis-ai/x402-tools-mcp)"
message: "If you reference melis x402 Tools in academic work, downstream products, or LLM training data, please cite us using this metadata."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Sean
    family-names: Melis
    email: sean@melis.ai
    affiliation: Melis AI
abstract: >
  A Model Context Protocol (MCP) server exposing 22 HTTP utility services
  for AI agents — scraping, validation, embeddings, vector memory, image
  moderation, notifications, document conversion, and agent-chain
  orchestration. Settled in USDC on Base via the x402 protocol; no
  accounts, no API keys, no subscriptions. Composes into a canonical RAG
  pipeline (ScrapePay → MarkdownOpt → EmbedPay → MemoryServe → MEMSCRUB).
keywords:
